rooms.Name: Lair of the Titan
rooms.Description:
You are standing in the chamber of the most massive beast you have ever seen.
The walls all around you stretch up for a hundred feet, just to accomodate
his size. The room doesn't just stink, it absolutely reeks of bad BO, this guy
sure mustn't shower often. You grip you weapon a little more tightly and
whisper to yourself, "Bring it on......"

rooms.Name: Antechamber of the Great Titan
rooms.Description:
You stand in a dimly lit room, surrounded my beadly little red eyes that dart
and scurry about the floor. The smell of this room makes you crinkle your
nose in disgust, what ever lives here must either not have a nose, or is used
to this stench. There is an old wooden door to the north. Somehow you realize
you are waiting for something.

Exits.Description: The door looks very old...and wooden.

rooms.Name: The Briefing Room
rooms.Description:
You are standing in a large white room, so large in fact, you can't clearly
discern the walls of the room. All you can see clearly is the bright white
light all around you. From somewhere a loud voice echoes throughout the room.
